{"tid":323354,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無絲巴依家係意大利-Venice","createTime":"2017-07-15T14:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T21:04:14.000Z","uid":103152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd905c5396ebf1dc43fd1da0765d885207e63ff","tid":323354,"uid":103152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"如題！有可以一齊有多個照應！<br />\n絕對唔介意係烈日當空下又流住汗水係景點幫你影靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一日到米蘭就爭少少俾人偷野，太危險<br />\n危險到要上黎搵旅伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb8beebb598d81d9ceb64b866fb3ef9e236aa99","tid":323354,"uid":103152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:18:01.000Z","msg":"順<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/221535_a7345a877f7448c2fccc2ba223d7bbbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F221535_a7345a877f7448c2fccc2ba223d7bbbc.jpg&h=d2ba2744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，米蘭好多手繩黨<br />\n見過幾個人中招，當俾左錢一個人，之後就會有幾個跟住問你拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747e345f0521d9848f6b32da034010f5082aef1e","tid":323354,"uid":23697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題！有可以一齊有多個照應！<br />\n絕對唔介意係烈日當空下又流住汗水係景點幫你影靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一日到米蘭就爭少少俾人偷野，太危險<br />\n危險到要上黎搵旅伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分享下點俾人偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e0dab3