normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一開始去左羅馬先 琴日去左五漁村<br />\n不過唔去米蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時感覺唔到意大利小偷既強勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有好多人都好好人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為係瑞士太安全，所以黎到太大對比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無去到Florence個outlet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbe7550f35661c2b923a6297ca5318490db5f03","tid":323354,"uid":17104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T18:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>18號過黎 到時仲係唔係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩走啦嗰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之後去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家係firenze<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁岩調轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去Florence-&gt;Rome</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全同你調轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一開始去左羅馬先 琴日去左五漁村<br />\n不過唔去米蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時感覺唔到意大利小偷既強勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有好多人都好好人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為係瑞士太安全，所以黎到太大對比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無去到Florence個outlet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係愛丁堡係安全到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎到呢到個袋係keep住放係前面同埋多人就捉實個袋<img src=\"/asse